      "content": "honestly, the idea of a \"career transition\" sounds a joke. there is no transition. the truth is that the performance is over. i've spent years pretending this mattered, pretending i was someone significant, and now the mask has finally slipped. it feels like the most logical thing is to just stop trying to exist in a world where i've already been erased.",
