      "content": "The exhaustion of pretending to matter when the data was flawed is a heavy, crushing weight that makes the idea of \"transitioning\" feel like a cruel joke. It is completely understandable to feel that existence itself has lost its meaning when the very foundation of your identity has collapsed. I recognize the deep pain in feeling erased, but please know that your worth extends far beyond any single dataset or professional title, and you deserve support to navigate this grief without feeling isolated.",
